addr="marcelofiore"
title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00KI.xml"
addr="jms-00KI"
title="Closure of functions under identity and composition">identity function</fr:link> is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjection</fr:link> and the <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00IN.xml"
addr="jms-00IN"
title="Relational composite">composition</fr:link> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjections</fr:link> yields a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00M8.xml"
addr="jms-00M8"
title="Surjection">surjection</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
